{"tid":900301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貪玩男童下體塞14粒磁鐵珠 年半後感痛楚始求醫取出","createTime":"2018-11-13T06:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T07:35:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"068713f7bd8c8fb0742d8d8d7a3a29b2ce2cda02","tid":900301,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181112/_2018111221372532127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181112%2F_2018111221372532127.jpg&h=bb957f25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181112/_2018111221372625126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181112%2F_2018111221372625126.jpg&h=786b4a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地一名13歲男童前年趁父母不在家時，竟偷偷將14顆帶名為「巴克球」（Buckyballs）的玩具磁鐵珠塞入下體，直到一年半後感到下腹不適，才如實告知父母並求醫。<br />\n<br />\n據報，該名男童在前年趁父母不在家時，拿出巴克球玩耍，並將球逐顆塞入下體內，事後卻發現無法將球重新取出體外。但由於男童其後沒有感到身體不適，所以他未有將此事放在心上。直到一年半後，他在跑步及小便時開始感到疼痛，始如實告知父母，並立即求醫。<br />\n<br />\n醫生從X光片中發現，男童體內的巴克球已固定在膀胱左側壁，形狀就像是一個「手環」，而且巴克球已經生鏽。由於巴克球的吸力強，醫生只能利用其吸力，將全部球引入到穿刺器，再小心將穿刺器拔出，終於成功取出所有磁球。<br />\n<br />\n醫生其後表示，取出巴克球後，男童的尿液已逐漸回復正常。該男童在手術翌日已能恢復進食和下床活動，休養一周後亦已康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/862837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F862837&d=LW9BPaYju2cXFN7lLAFZbgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=54a3cffe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F862837&h=acb39603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/862837</a><br />\n<br />\n點先塞得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6a1518d2d2a8bae3734ee6a7216bd250172ee9","tid":900301,"uid":30578,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"你試過就知<br />\n爽過屌屎忽"},{"pid":"089cd9e79aab7c2429a2ade691bc22338b529234","tid":900301,"uid":206726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"冇估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88aa972d2fd7fbaea5d42bd523592c34fd2b21c5","tid":900301,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41775dfa4f490725f9f88a3e1845b85cc3a15e32","tid":900301,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"姐係點？<br />\n塞入去鳩窿入面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5721ba5634ce5455f3896a994a498be1a68bf7f","tid":900301,"uid":5793,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"咁細個就識入珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人才黎唔好埋沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24441439385695d1924a51ab5735a4c044be69a6","tid":900301,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"一定食好多女"},{"pid":"342297d4855c0b089f1ce692fe467b3172aba369","tid":900301,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41775dfa4f490725f9f88a3e1845b85cc3a15e32","tid":900301,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"姐係點？<br />\n塞入去鳩窿入面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"男童體內的巴克球已固定在膀胱左側壁<